-- Hungary Prepares to Cut Public Sector Jobs by 5-10%, Napi Gazdasag Reports
-- B y   Z o l t a n   S i m o n
-- 2010-10-12T05:46:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/hungary-prepares-to-cut-public-sector-jobs-by-5-10-napi-gazdasag-reports.html
Hungary is preparing to cut staff
levels at budget-funded institutions by 5 percent and at
supporting institutions by a further 10 percent,  Napi Gazdasag 
reported, citing Jozsef Feher, secretary-general of the
Hungarian Civil Servants Association.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Zoltan Simon  in Budapest at 
 zsimon@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Willy Morris at 
 wmorris@bloomberg.net . 